channel.title: DFS Model
channel.description: When I walk around with a dfs on, it floats. I heard you have to do something with the model like un g zip it or something. I was wondering if anyone knew what to do with it. I found the "fixed" models on some site and uploaded them (http://uppit.com/6BUOSO) can someone explain what to do with this? Thanks a bunch.

item.title: DFS Model
item.dc:creator: @Coder_Kieran Coder Kieran
item.description:
@Coder_Kieran wrote:

With these models, you download them and extract them into your models folder.
then in-game say out loud

addmodel (id)

then once all are added, restart your client.
